headline: Is CoStar Group’s 29% Rally in 2025 Backed by Strong Fundamentals?
summary: Trying to decide what to do with CoStar Group stock? You’re certainly not alone. With its impressive footprint in real estate data and analytics, CoStar often lands on investor watchlists. But before you make any moves, it’s worth taking a closer look at how the market has been sizing up the stock lately. Over the past quarter, CSGP shares are up over 23%, and year to date, they’re sporting nearly a 29% gain. This isn’t just noise, as there is real momentum here, partly reflecting optimism...
